comment: Russell (LAL) does not extend his arm or go through the space of Dragic (LAL) as he stops and creates space.

Whiteside (MIA) cleanly knocks the ball away from Clarkson (LAL).
Randle (LAL) does not release the shot attempt prior to the shot clock expiring.
Nance Jr. (LAL) sets the screen on Deng (MIA) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that Randle's (LAL) shot attempt was released after the shot clock had expired was upheld.
